---
title: Posts
layout: default
pageOrder: 2
---

each doc in getCollection('posts').toJSON()
  article.post
    header
      h1
        a(href=doc.url)= doc.title
      p.meta
        = doc.date.toShortDateString()
    section.content
      | !{helper.summary(doc.contentRenderedWithoutLayouts)}
      a(href=doc.url) Read more &raquo;